<NomaiObject>
	<TextBlock>
		<ID>1</ID>
		<Text>
			MELORAE: The heat from this star system’s <![CDATA[<color=lightblue>sun</color>]]> is more bearable below the surface.
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>

	<TextBlock>
		<ID>2</ID>
		<Text>
			MELORAE: When our <![CDATA[<color=orange>escape pod</color>]]> punctured this planet’s surface, it broke into what scans show is a cave system with much cooler air. I <![CDATA[<i>would</i>]]> recommend we seek a site down there to build a long-term shelter, Annona, but these passages are a maze!
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>

	<TextBlock>
		<ID>3</ID>
		<Text>
			ANNONA: Even with this danger, they are still our best chance for survival. We’ll form teams and descend into the caves to look for a shelter site. We can mark our findings on the walls to avoid becoming irreversibly lost.
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>

	<TextBlock>
		<ID>4</ID>
		<Text>
			ANNONA: Be cautious, everyone.
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>

	<TextBlock>
		<ID>5</ID>
		<Text>
			RHUS: And be aware of the sand as you search. It appears to be rising gradually.
		</Text>
	</TextBlock>

